{"id":156,"ayahs":[{"number":44,"arabic":"وَنَادَىٰٓ أَصْحَٰبُ ٱلْجَنَّةِ أَصْحَٰبَ ٱلنَّارِ أَن قَدْ وَجَدْنَا مَا وَعَدَنَا رَبُّنَا حَقًّۭا فَهَلْ وَجَدتُّم مَّا وَعَدَ رَبُّكُمْ حَقًّۭا ۖ قَالُوا۟ نَعَمْ ۚ فَأَذَّنَ مُؤَذِّنٌۢ بَيْنَهُمْ أَن لَّعْنَةُ ٱللَّهِ عَلَى ٱلظَّٰلِمِينَ","translation":"And the inmates of paradise will call out to the inmates of the fire: \"Now we have found that what our Sustainer promised us has come true; have you. too, found that what your Sustainer promised you has come true?\" [The others] will answer, \"Yes!\"-whereupon from their midst a voice will loudly proclaim: \"God's rejection is the due of the evildoers","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/998.mp3","surahId":7,"words":[{"id":44127,"position":1,"arabic":"وَنَادَىٰٓ","translation":"এবং ডেকে বলবে","audioUrl":"wbw/007_044_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":44128,"position":2,"arabic":"أَصْحَـٰبُ","translation":"অধিবাসীরা","audioUrl":"wbw/007_044_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":44129,"position":3,"arabic":"ٱلْجَنَّةِ","translation":"জান্নাতের","audioUrl":"wbw/007_044_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":44130,"position":4,"arabic":"أَصْحَـٰبَ","translation":"অধিবাসীদেরকে","audioUrl":"wbw/007_044_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":44131,"position":5,"arabic":"ٱلنَّارِ","translation":"আগুনের","audioUrl":"wbw/007_044_005.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":44132,"position":6,"arabic":"أَن","translation":"যে","audioUrl":"wbw/007_044_006.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":44133,"position":7,"arabic":"قَدْ","translation":"\"নিশ্চয়ই","audioUrl":"wbw/007_044_007.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":44134,"position":8,"arabic":"وَجَدْنَا","translation":"আমরা পেয়েছি","audioUrl":"wbw/007_044_008.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":44135,"position":9,"arabic":"مَا","translation":"যা","audioUrl":"wbw/007_044_009.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":44136,"position":10,"arabic":"وَعَدَنَا","translation":"প্রতিশ্রুতি দিয়েছিলেন আমাদের","audioUrl":"wbw/007_044_010.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":44137,"position":11,"arabic":"رَبُّنَا","translation":"রব আমাদের","audioUrl":"wbw/007_044_011.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":44138,"position":12,"arabic":"حَقًّۭا","translation":"সত্য হিসেবে","audioUrl":"wbw/007_044_012.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":44139,"position":13,"arabic":"فَهَلْ","translation":"কিন্তু কি","audioUrl":"wbw/007_044_013.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":44140,"position":14,"arabic":"وَجَدتُّم","translation":"তোমরা পেয়েছো","audioUrl":"wbw/007_044_014.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":44141,"position":15,"arabic":"مَّا","translation":"যা","audioUrl":"wbw/007_044_015.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":44142,"position":16,"arabic":"وَعَدَ","translation":"প্রতিশ্রুতি দিয়েছিলেন","audioUrl":"wbw/007_044_016.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":44143,"position":17,"arabic":"رَبُّكُمْ","translation":"রব তোমাদের","audioUrl":"wbw/007_044_017.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":44144,"position":18,"arabic":"حَقًّۭا ۖ","translation":"সত্য হিসেবে\"","audioUrl":"wbw/007_044_018.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":44146,"position":19,"arabic":"قَالُوا۟","translation":"তারা বলবে","audioUrl":"wbw/007_044_020.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":44147,"position":20,"arabic":"نَعَمْ ۚ","translation":"\"হ্যাঁ\"","audioUrl":"wbw/007_044_021.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":44149,"position":21,"arabic":"فَأَذَّنَ","translation":"অতঃপর ঘোষণা দেবে","audioUrl":"wbw/007_044_023.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":44150,"position":22,"arabic":"مُؤَذِّنٌۢ","translation":"এক ঘোষণাকারী","audioUrl":"wbw/007_044_024.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":44151,"position":23,"arabic":"بَيْنَهُمْ","translation":"মাঝে তাদের","audioUrl":"wbw/007_044_025.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":44152,"position":24,"arabic":"أَن","translation":"যে","audioUrl":"wbw/007_044_026.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":44153,"position":25,"arabic":"لَّعْنَةُ","translation":"\"অভিশাপ","audioUrl":"wbw/007_044_027.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":44154,"position":26,"arabic":"ٱللَّهِ","translation":"আল্লাহর","audioUrl":"wbw/007_044_028.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":44155,"position":27,"arabic":"عَلَى","translation":"উপর","audioUrl":"wbw/007_044_029.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":44156,"position":28,"arabic":"ٱلظَّـٰلِمِينَ","translation":"সীমালঙ্ঘনকারীদের","audioUrl":"wbw/007_044_030.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":44157,"position":29,"arabic":"٤٤","translation":"(৪৪)","audioUrl":null,"charTypeName":"end"}]},{"number":45,"arabic":"ٱلَّذِينَ يَصُدُّونَ عَن سَبِيلِ ٱللَّهِ وَيَبْغُونَهَا عِوَجًۭا وَهُم بِٱلْءَاخِرَةِ كَٰفِرُونَ","translation":"who turn others away from God's path and try to make it appear crooked, and who refuse to acknowledge the truth of the life to come!\"","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/999.mp3","surahId":7,"words":[{"id":45121,"position":1,"arabic":"ٱلَّذِينَ","translation":"যারা","audioUrl":"wbw/007_045_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":45122,"position":2,"arabic":"يَصُدُّونَ","translation":"(মানুষকে) বাধা দিতো","audioUrl":"wbw/007_045_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":45123,"position":3,"arabic":"عَن","translation":"হতে","audioUrl":"wbw/007_045_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":45124,"position":4,"arabic":"سَبِيلِ","translation":"পথ","audioUrl":"wbw/007_045_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":45125,"position":5,"arabic":"ٱللَّهِ","translation":"আল্লাহর","audioUrl":"wbw/007_045_005.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":45126,"position":6,"arabic":"وَيَبْغُونَهَا","translation":"ও তারা অনুসন্ধান করতো তাতে","audioUrl":"wbw/007_045_006.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":45127,"position":7,"arabic":"عِوَجًۭا","translation":"বক্রতা","audioUrl":"wbw/007_045_007.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":45128,"position":8,"arabic":"وَهُم","translation":"আর তারা (ছিলো)","audioUrl":"wbw/007_045_008.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":45129,"position":9,"arabic":"بِٱلْـَٔاخِرَةِ","translation":"উপর আখিরাতের","audioUrl":"wbw/007_045_009.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":45130,"position":10,"arabic":"كَـٰفِرُونَ","translation":"অবিশ্বাসী\"","audioUrl":"wbw/007_045_010.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":45131,"position":11,"arabic":"٤٥","translation":"(৪৫)","audioUrl":null,"charTypeName":"end"}]},{"number":46,"arabic":"وَبَيْنَهُمَا حِجَابٌۭ ۚ وَعَلَى ٱلْأَعْرَافِ رِجَالٌۭ يَعْرِفُونَ كُلًّۢا بِسِيمَىٰهُمْ ۚ وَنَادَوْا۟ أَصْحَٰبَ ٱلْجَنَّةِ أَن سَلَٰمٌ عَلَيْكُمْ ۚ لَمْ يَدْخُلُوهَا وَهُمْ يَطْمَعُونَ","translation":"And between the two there will be a barrier. And there will be persons who [in life] were endowed with the faculty of discernment [between right and wrong], recognizing each by its mark. And they will call out unto the inmates of paradise, \"Peace be upon you!\"-not having entered it themselves, but longing [for it].","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/1000.mp3","surahId":7,"words":[{"id":45606,"position":1,"arabic":"وَبَيْنَهُمَا","translation":"এবং মাঝে উভয়ের","audioUrl":"wbw/007_046_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":45607,"position":2,"arabic":"حِجَابٌۭ ۚ","translation":"পর্দা","audioUrl":"wbw/007_046_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":45609,"position":3,"arabic":"وَعَلَى","translation":"এবং উপর (থাকবে)","audioUrl":"wbw/007_046_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":45610,"position":4,"arabic":"ٱلْأَعْرَافِ","translation":"আ'রাফের","audioUrl":"wbw/007_046_005.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":45611,"position":5,"arabic":"رِجَالٌۭ","translation":"কিছু লোক","audioUrl":"wbw/007_046_006.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":45612,"position":6,"arabic":"يَعْرِفُونَ","translation":"তারা চিনবে","audioUrl":"wbw/007_046_007.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":45613,"position":7,"arabic":"كُلًّۢا","translation":"প্রত্যেককে","audioUrl":"wbw/007_046_008.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":45614,"position":8,"arabic":"بِسِيمَىٰهُمْ ۚ","translation":"মাধ্যমে চিহ্নগুলো তাদের","audioUrl":"wbw/007_046_009.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":45616,"position":9,"arabic":"وَنَادَوْا۟","translation":"এবং তারা ডেকে বলবে","audioUrl":"wbw/007_046_011.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":45617,"position":10,"arabic":"أَصْحَـٰبَ","translation":"অধিবাসীদেরকে","audioUrl":"wbw/007_046_012.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":45618,"position":11,"arabic":"ٱلْجَنَّةِ","translation":"জান্নাতের","audioUrl":"wbw/007_046_013.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":45619,"position":12,"arabic":"أَن","translation":"যে","audioUrl":"wbw/007_046_014.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":45620,"position":13,"arabic":"سَلَـٰمٌ","translation":"\"শান্তি","audioUrl":"wbw/007_046_015.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":45621,"position":14,"arabic":"عَلَيْكُمْ ۚ","translation":"উপর তোমাদের (বর্ষিত হোক)\"","audioUrl":"wbw/007_046_016.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":45623,"position":15,"arabic":"لَمْ","translation":"নি","audioUrl":"wbw/007_046_018.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":45624,"position":16,"arabic":"يَدْخُلُوهَا","translation":"তাতে প্রবেশ করেন (তারা এখনও)","audioUrl":"wbw/007_046_019.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":45625,"position":17,"arabic":"وَهُمْ","translation":"কিন্তু তারা","audioUrl":"wbw/007_046_020.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":45626,"position":18,"arabic":"يَطْمَعُونَ","translation":"তারা আশা করে","audioUrl":"wbw/007_046_021.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":45627,"position":19,"arabic":"٤٦","translation":"(৪৬)","audioUrl":null,"charTypeName":"end"}]},{"number":47,"arabic":"۞ وَإِذَا صُرِفَتْ أَبْصَٰرُهُمْ تِلْقَآءَ أَصْحَٰبِ ٱلنَّارِ قَالُوا۟ رَبَّنَا لَا تَجْعَلْنَا مَعَ ٱلْقَوْمِ ٱلظَّٰلِمِينَ","translation":"And whenever their eyes are turned towards the inmates of the fire, they will cry: \"O our Sustainer! Place us not among the people who have been guilty of evildoing!\"","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/1001.mp3","surahId":7,"words":[{"id":46405,"position":1,"arabic":"۞ وَإِذَا","translation":"এবং যখন","audioUrl":"wbw/007_047_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":46406,"position":2,"arabic":"صُرِفَتْ","translation":"ফিরানো হবে","audioUrl":"wbw/007_047_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":46407,"position":3,"arabic":"أَبْصَـٰرُهُمْ","translation":"দৃষ্টিগুলো তাদের","audioUrl":"wbw/007_047_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":46408,"position":4,"arabic":"تِلْقَآءَ","translation":"দিকে","audioUrl":"wbw/007_047_005.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":46409,"position":5,"arabic":"أَصْحَـٰبِ","translation":"অধিবাসীদের","audioUrl":"wbw/007_047_006.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":46410,"position":6,"arabic":"ٱلنَّارِ","translation":"(জাহান্নামের) আগুনের","audioUrl":"wbw/007_047_007.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":46411,"position":7,"arabic":"قَالُوا۟","translation":"তারা বলবে","audioUrl":"wbw/007_047_008.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":46412,"position":8,"arabic":"رَبَّنَا","translation":"\"হে আমাদের রব","audioUrl":"wbw/007_047_009.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":46413,"position":9,"arabic":"لَا","translation":"না","audioUrl":"wbw/007_047_010.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":46414,"position":10,"arabic":"تَجْعَلْنَا","translation":"আমাদের করো","audioUrl":"wbw/007_047_011.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":46415,"position":11,"arabic":"مَعَ","translation":"সাথে","audioUrl":"wbw/007_047_012.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":46416,"position":12,"arabic":"ٱلْقَوْمِ","translation":"(ঐসব) সম্প্রদায়ের","audioUrl":"wbw/007_047_013.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":46417,"position":13,"arabic":"ٱلظَّـٰلِمِينَ","translation":"(যারা) সীমালঙ্ঘনকারী\"","audioUrl":"wbw/007_047_014.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":46418,"position":14,"arabic":"٤٧","translation":"(৪৭)","audioUrl":null,"charTypeName":"end"}]},{"number":48,"arabic":"وَنَادَىٰٓ أَصْحَٰبُ ٱلْأَعْرَافِ رِجَالًۭا يَعْرِفُونَهُم بِسِيمَىٰهُمْ قَالُوا۟ مَآ أَغْنَىٰ عَنكُمْ جَمْعُكُمْ وَمَا كُنتُمْ تَسْتَكْبِرُونَ","translation":"And they who [in life] had possessed this faculty of discernment will call out to those whom they recognize by their marks [as sinners], saying: \"What has your amassing [of wealth] availed you, and all the false pride of your past?","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/1002.mp3","surahId":7,"words":[{"id":47001,"position":1,"arabic":"وَنَادَىٰٓ","translation":"এবং ডাকবে","audioUrl":"wbw/007_048_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":47002,"position":2,"arabic":"أَصْحَـٰبُ","translation":"অধিবাসীরা","audioUrl":"wbw/007_048_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":47003,"position":3,"arabic":"ٱلْأَعْرَافِ","translation":"আ'রাফের","audioUrl":"wbw/007_048_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":47004,"position":4,"arabic":"رِجَالًۭا","translation":"(দোযখের কিছু) লোকদেরকে","audioUrl":"wbw/007_048_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":47005,"position":5,"arabic":"يَعْرِفُونَهُم","translation":"তারা চিনবে তাদের","audioUrl":"wbw/007_048_005.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":47006,"position":6,"arabic":"بِسِيمَىٰهُمْ","translation":"মাধ্যমে চিহ্নগুলো তাদের","audioUrl":"wbw/007_048_006.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":47007,"position":7,"arabic":"قَالُوا۟","translation":"তারা বলবে","audioUrl":"wbw/007_048_007.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":47008,"position":8,"arabic":"مَآ","translation":"\"না","audioUrl":"wbw/007_048_008.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":47009,"position":9,"arabic":"أَغْنَىٰ","translation":"কাজে আসল","audioUrl":"wbw/007_048_009.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":47010,"position":10,"arabic":"عَنكُمْ","translation":"জন্যে তোমাদের","audioUrl":"wbw/007_048_010.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":47011,"position":11,"arabic":"جَمْعُكُمْ","translation":"দলবল তোমাদের","audioUrl":"wbw/007_048_011.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":47012,"position":12,"arabic":"وَمَا","translation":"ও যা (নিয়ে)","audioUrl":"wbw/007_048_012.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":47013,"position":13,"arabic":"كُنتُمْ","translation":"তোমরা ছিলে","audioUrl":"wbw/007_048_013.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":47014,"position":14,"arabic":"تَسْتَكْبِرُونَ","translation":"তোমরা ঔদ্ধত্য প্রকাশ করতে\"","audioUrl":"wbw/007_048_014.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":47015,"position":15,"arabic":"٤٨","translation":"(৪৮)","audioUrl":